    <abstract>
      <p>cyjShiny is an open-source R package that allows users to embed network visualization into Shiny apps and R Markdown documents. cyjShiny (<ext-link xlink:href="https://github.com/cytoscape/cyjShiny" ext-link-type="uri">https://github.com/cytoscape/cyjShiny</ext-link>) builds on the cytoscape.js Javascript graph library. Additionally, the package provides helper functions to convert common R data representations (e.g., data.frame) into forms compatible with cytoscape.js.</p>
    </abstract>
